						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken stone set up in the gate-way of the temple of Hanumān.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record registers a gift, probably of money, for burning lights before a god (name lost). It is engraved in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">14th century A.D.</hi></p>						

